      "data": "ਕਰਿ ਕਿਰਪਾ; ਲੀਨੇ ਲੜਿ ਲਾਏ ॥",
      "page": 744,
      "line": 12
    },
    {
      "asset": "sbms",
      "type": "translation",
      "language": "en",
      "data": "Showing mercy, the Lord has attached me to His skirt."
    },
    {
      "asset": "sbms",
      "type": "translation",
      "language": "pa",
      "data": "ਮਿਹਰ ਧਾਰ ਕੇ, ਸਾਈਂ ਨੇ ਮੈਂਨੂੰ ਆਪਣੇ ਪੱਲੇ ਨਾਲ ਲਾ ਲਿਆ ਹੈ।"
    },
    {
      "asset": "dssk",
      "type": "translation",
      "language": "en",
      "data": "Showering His Mercy, he has attached me to the hem of His robe."
    },
    {
      "asset": "nkft",
      "type": "translation",
      "language": "pa",
      "data": "ਕਿਰਪਾ ਕਰ ਕੇ ਚਰਨੀ ਲਾਇ ਲੀਏ ਹਾਂ॥"
    },
    {
      "asset": "psst",
      "type": "translation",
      "language": "pa",
      "data": "ਮੇਹਰ ਕਰ ਕੇ ਜਿਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਨੂੰ ਪ੍ਰਭੂ ਆਪਣੇ ਲੜ ਲਾ ਲੈਂਦਾ ਹੈ,"
    },
    {
      "asset": "snst",
      "type": "translation",
      "language": "es",
      "data": "El Señor, en Su Misericordia, me deja aferrarme a Su Túnica."
